title: The Mortal Kombat Konquest
itunes:title: The Mortal Kombat Konquest
description:
After launching in 1992, Mortal Kombat would spawn a massive franchise. It would also burn out the creators of the franchise and the company that spawned it would go out of business. And yet the tournament survives!
